title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 25 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 25 2022
description:
Dr. Oz joins Clay and Buck to discuss his Senate run in Pennsylvania and how he secured President Trump's endorsement. C&B don't take sides in GOP primaries, offer platform to all major GOP candidates in big races. WaPo's lame defense for outing Libs of TikTok. Parents outraged by teachers and schools pushing transgenderism on children. Breaking news: Elon Musk officially buys Twitter.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
